                <h4>About BuH</h4>
                <p>BuH (Better UB Hub) is a class registration system that aims for a simple and intuitive experience. Click the link below to try out BuH for yourself.</p>
                <h4>Testing</h4>
                <p>
                    While testing BuH you will assume the role of a student registering for classes. Please take note and report any design features which you liked or disliked. If something did not make sense, please let us know by following the link below to our issues page.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Most importantly, if you encounter errors or features not working correctly, please submit a report with as much information as you can provide (what you were trying to accomplish, what went wrong, etc)
                    and screenshots if possible.
                </p>
                <h4>Features/What To Test</h4>
                BuH currently supports the following features for use:<br />
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Logging In As A Student
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Student Dashboard Containing Useful Information About Your Enrollment
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Ability to Enroll In Courses (by default, two courses, each with a recitation, are available to enroll in)
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Ability to Drop from Courses Currently Enrolled In
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Ability To Search For Courses (Enrollment) With Various Sorting Methods
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Calendar-View Of Enrolled Course Schedule
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>After you've completed your testing, we'd love for you to fill out our <a class="btn btn-warning btn-lg" href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=1KHiDYwOG41D6t1Pk33EkAIIz5NUp48UAfmjfwIrGroU">Beta Test Feedback Survey &raquo;</a></p>
                <br/>
                <h4>Reporting Issues</h4>
                <p>Find a bug in our application? Head over to our <a href="https://github.com/vanpyrzericj/Alphon/issues">GitHub Issues Page</a> and file a new issue. When filing an issue, please be descriptive about the error (what did you click, what were you doing leading up to the error). Please also include the date and time the error occurred, so we can check it against our internal data collection tools.</p>
                <br/>
                <h4>Want to Contribute?</h4>
                <p>Of course you do. Get it? Head over to our <a href="https://github.com/vanpyrzericj/Alphon/wiki/Developer-Contributions-(Onboarding)">onboarding wiki page</a> to see how to get our application up and running on a local environment.</p>
